<section>
  <h2 id="basic-flex">Basic Flex Layout</h2>
  <p>
    A flex layout is initiated with the <code>.d-flex</code> class. By default,
    <code>display: flex;</code> creates a non-wrapping row. Use <code>.fd-column</code> to create a
    column layout.
  </p>

  <h3>Basic Examples</h3>
